\c 18
\p
\v 1 Ozehlukanisayo udinga okuloyisekayo \add kwakhe\add*; ufohlela\x + 17.14.\x* inhlakanipho yonke\x + Jobe 5.12.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Isithutha kasithokozi ekuqedisiseni, kodwa ukuze inhliziyo yaso iziveze\x + 10.19. 13.16. Tshu. 10.3.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Lapho okhohlakeleyo esiza, kuza lokudelela, njalo kanye lenhloni, ihlazo.
\p
\v 4 Amazwi omlomo womuntu\x + 10.11.\x* angamanzi azikileyo\x + 20.5.\x*; umthombo wenhlakanipho uyisifula esigobhozayo\x + Hlab. 78.2. Joha. 7.38. Hlab. 145.7.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Kakulunganga ukwemukela ubuso bokhohlakeleyo\x + 24.23. Hlab. 82.2. Levi 19.15. Dute. 10.17.\x*, ukuphambula olungileyo kusahlulelo\x + 17.15. Dute. 16.18.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Indebe zesithutha zingena enkanini, lomlomo waso ubiza imivimvinya\x + 19.29.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Umlomo wesithutha uyintshabalalo yaso, lendebe zaso zingumjibila womphefumulo waso\x + 12.13. 13.3. 10.14. Hlab. 59.12. 64.8. 140.9. Tshu. 10.12.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Amazwi onyeyayo anjengezibondlo\x + 26.22.\x* ezehlela kokungaphakathi kwesisu\x + 26.22.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lolivila emsebenzini wakhe ungumfowabo\x + 28.24.\x* womchithi\x + 3.27. 22.24.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* lingumphotshongo oqinileyo; olungileyo uzagijimela kuwo amiswe phezulu evikelekile\x + Hlab. 61.3. 2 Sam. 22.3,51. Hlab. 18.2. 27.1.91.2. 144.2.\x*.
