\v 11 Inotho yesinothi ingumuzi waso oqinileyo\x + 10.15.\x*, lanjengomthangala ophakemeyo ekucabangeni kwaso\x + 25.11. Hlab. 73.7.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Mandulo kokubhujiswa inhliziyo yomuntu iyaziphakamisa\x + 29.23.\x*, njalo mandulo kodumo kulokuthobeka\x + 15.33.\x*.
