\v 13 Ophendula indaba engakezwa, kuyibuwula kuye, lehlazo\x + Joha. 7.51.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Umoya womuntu uzasekela ukugula kwakhe, kodwa umoya owephukileyo, ngubani ongawuthwala\x + 15.13.\x*?
\p
\v 15 Inhliziyo yoqedisisayo izuza ulwazi, lendlebe yabahlakaniphileyo idinga ulwazi\x + 8.22.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Isipho somuntu siyamvulela ngokubanzi, simkhokhelela phambi kwabakhulu\x + 17.8. Gen. 32.20. 1 Sam. 25.27. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ongowokuqala ecaleni lakhe \add ubonakala\add* elungile, kodwa umakhelwane wakhe ufika amhlole\x + Mat. 7.5.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Inkatho iqeda izingxabano, yehlukanise phakathi kwabalamandla.
\p
\v 19 Umzalwane owoniweyo wedlula umuzi oqinileyo, lengxabano zinjengomgoqo wenqaba\x + Isa. 25.2.\x*.
